  "parts": [
    {"part_id": "pillar_a_right", "status": "damaged", "damage_level": "severe", "damage_types": ["deformation"], "confidence": "high", "model_confidence_score": 0.85, "description": "右A柱顶部严重变形"}
  ]
}
```

只输出 JSON，不要额外文字。只评估候选清单内的部件。
